article.headline: Sibley scores 18, Southern Utah downs Western New Mexico 96-68
article.description: — Jamari Sibley had 18 points in Southern Utah's 96-68 victory against Western New Mexico on Monday.
article.linkText: Sibley scores 18, Southern Utah downs Western New Mexico 96-68
article.story: CEDAR CITY, Utah -- — Jamari Sibley had 18 points in Southern Utah's 96-68 victory against Western New Mexico on Monday. Sibley also contributed 10 rebounds and three blocks for the Thunderbirds. Tavi Jackson shot 6 of 10 from the field and 3 of 4 from the free-throw line to add 15 points. Brock Felder, Hercy Miller and Dominique Ford all had 12 points. The Mustangs were led by Yves Nkomba and Carson Kell with 13 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
